Norwegian Broker Arctic Opens Office in Brazil, DN Reports

-- B y   S t e p h e n   T r e l o a r
-- 
2011-05-26T06:41:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/norwegian-broker-arctic-opens-office-in-brazil-dn-reports.html
Norwegian broker Arctic Securities
ASA will open its first overseas office in  Rio de Janeiro  to
serve clients in the offshore industry, Dagens Naeringsliv
reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Mads Syversen.  TC Hoeiseth and Hans Bollingmo will head the office, which
will be the first for a Norwegian securities firm in  Brazil , the
Oslo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Treloar at 
 streloar1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
